BEGIN:VJOURNAL
UID:journal-1@example.com
DTSTAMP:20260601T090000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260601
SUMMARY:Week 1 Planning Notes
DESCRIPTION:Decided to focus on the command palette feature this sprint. Met with design to review mockups. Key decisions: Use cmdk for the base library\, support natural language input\, add keyboard navigation for all actions.
CATEGORIES:WORK
END:VJOURNAL

BEGIN:VJOURNAL
UID:journal-2@example.com
DTSTAMP:20260605T183000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260605
SUMMARY:Work Retreat Takeaways
DESCRIPTION:Great team building session at the resort. Teams were restructured for the next quarter. Introduced new sprint methodology. Everyone seems energized about the product roadmap. Action items from the retreat need to be added to the project board.
CATEGORIES:WORK,PERSONAL
END:VJOURNAL

BEGIN:VJOURNAL
UID:journal-3@example.com
DTSTAMP:20260610T210000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260610
SUMMARY:Anniversary Dinner Reflections
DESCRIPTION:Wonderful evening at Italian Place Downtown. Sarah loved the surprise. We talked about our goals for the second half of the year. Thinking about planning a trip to Italy later this year.
CATEGORIES:PERSONAL
END:VJOURNAL

BEGIN:VJOURNAL
UID:journal-4@example.com
DTSTAMP:20260615T080000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260615
SUMMARY:Mid-Month Review
DESCRIPTION:Progress check on Q2 goals. Done: Command palette MVP shipped\, CalDAV sync improvements deployed\, documentation updated. In Progress: Mobile responsiveness improvements\, recurring event UI overhaul. Blocked: Waiting on design tokens from the design system team. Overall on track but need to pick up pace on mobile work.
CATEGORIES:WORK
END:VJOURNAL

BEGIN:VJOURNAL
UID:journal-5@example.com
DTSTAMP:20260620T190000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260620
SUMMARY:Vacation Planning
DESCRIPTION:Explored options for the family trip to the lake house. Cabin rental confirmed for June 24-26. Need to pack fishing gear\, board games\, sunscreen. Grocery run planned for Wednesday evening. Mom offered to water the plants while we are away.
CATEGORIES:PERSONAL,TRAVEL
END:VJOURNAL

BEGIN:VJOURNAL
UID:journal-6@example.com
DTSTAMP:20260625T170000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260625
SUMMARY:Product Ideas Brainstorm
DESCRIPTION:After the product planning workshop\, some ideas worth exploring: Calendar sharing with family view. Quick-add natural language for tasks. Integration with todoist. Dark mode improvements with more theme options. Export to PDF for printing. Need to validate these with user research before committing.
CATEGORIES:WORK,IDEAS
END:VJOURNAL

BEGIN:VJOURNAL
UID:journal-7@example.com
DTSTAMP:20260630T160000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260630
SUMMARY:Month-End Reflections
DESCRIPTION:June was a productive month. Key accomplishments: Shipped command palette feature\, fixed several recurring event bugs\, improved dark mode support\, team morale is high after the retreat. Areas to improve: Better test coverage for edge cases\, more comprehensive documentation\, automate more of the release process. Looking forward to July and the mobile redesign sprint.
CATEGORIES:WORK,PERSONAL
END:VJOURNAL

END:VCALENDAR
